    "content": "<p>Was a pleasure facilitating one of my \"live AI cooking shows\" ‚Äî we built an end-to-end system:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>voice agent that could conduct hundreds of interviews w employees on demand,</li>\n<li>gather and analyze organizational health data based on the transcripts, and</li>\n<li>generate executive summaries as both Amazon-style memos (for tech leadership) and slides (even w a script for a presenter to record a charismatic Loom video on top!).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Any HR leaders who'd be interested in getting comprehensive, actionable data on employee satisfaction and org health in minutes, not months, just send me a DM...</p>\n<p>Thanks for hosting Daniel Lee</p>\n",
