    "title": "Excited to join other speakers like Mark Cuban at the 2025 Global Entrepreneurship Network Congress this June!",
    "date": "2025-04-07",
    "content": "<p>Excited to join other speakers like Mark Cuban at the 2025 Global Entrepreneurship Network Congress this June!</p>\n<p>I'll be doing one of my live \"AI cooking shows,\" inviting one lucky participant to the stage to create something with AI* that would normally take 2 weeks + a team of specialists in less than two hours.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>recent working session outputs:</li>\n<li>hyper-tailored marketing campaign + funnel via Lovable, including a <a href=\"https://vapi.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vapi</a> AI assistant with the CEO's ElevenLabs cloned voice behind a phone number, ready to give guidance to prospects via a long-form discovery conversation, trained on key know-how (e.g., tacit knowledge from the founders thanks to Granola, company blog posts scraped instantaneously via Firecrawl and incorporated into AI memory);</li>\n<li>an AI-powered system that drafts bills-of-materials derived from customer requirements-gathering Ambient call transcripts, uses Google's Gemini 2.5 Pro to qa/qc BOM iterations and catch errors upstream, was all turned into a custom web application that hooks into the OpenAI API thanks to the Replit v2 Agent, and generates a crisp, on-brand Gamma update deck for the CoS to send to the VP Ops; and</li>\n<li>a voice-driven HR Pulse survey that CHROs can deploy on-demand, use to collect hundreds of hours of employee feedback (each highly personalized with probing questions generated on-the-fly and in line with the c-suite's strategic direction!), and then analyze in minutes, not months via state-of-the-art reasoning models...</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All these from just the past two weeks ‚Äî given the technology development curve we're on, who knows what will be possible by June :)</p>\n<p>Get your ticket and join entrepreneurs and innovators from over 200 countries today:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lnkd.in/dR7bfzZy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://lnkd.in/dR7bfzZy</a></p>\n",
