    "content": "<p>Gamma is my favorite new AI tool.</p>\n<p>Just shelled out for the paid account.</p>\n<p>Super underrated; check it out: capture a rich conversation, unpack it with next steps via a thought partnership with OpenAI's <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> <a href=\"https://o1.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">o1 Pro</a> + Deep Research‚Äîthen, decompose where you land into a spec for Gamma, and record a script-driven presentation via Loom that you can deliver back to stakeholders with a clear CTA button (e.g., to a bespoke voice assistant to continue the conversation, a Stripe link to pay for some work product, a meeting booking link).</p>\n<p>Rich, precise, async communication and collaboration has arrived.</p>\n",
