    "date": "2025-02-12",
    "content": "<p>I had an absolute blast speaking on the OKR mentors panel last week about Strategy, Execution, and AI with some stellar practitioners: Elie, Harry, Natalie, and Peter.</p>\n<p>Huge thanks to Elie and the entire OKR Mentors team for hosting such a dynamic conversation!</p>\n<p>While I can‚Äôt share the full panel (it‚Äôs part of the complete OKR Forum event recap), I‚Äôve pulled together some of my biggest takeaways in a new article‚Äîespecially on how AI supercharges OKRs and can help you move from idea to execution at unprecedented speed.</p>\n<p>Read the full article here for insights on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Leveraging AI for rapid ‚Äúfront-end intelligence‚Äù</li>\n<li>Building quick, low-cost product prototypes</li>\n<li>Avoiding ‚Äúshadow AI‚Äù and other pitfalls</li>\n<li>My favorite prompt to spark next-level strategic thinking</li>\n</ul>\n",
