    "id": "post-2024-12-18-7275142603367493633",
    "title": "Do you know you need to cultivate a personal brand but are anxious about posting?",
    "date": "2024-12-18",
    "content": "<p>Do you know you need to cultivate a personal brand but are anxious about posting?</p>\n<p>Imagine if, instead of dealing with a blank page problem, you could call a phone number, and on the other end was an expert interviewer who knew everything about you.</p>\n<p>This person would have infinite patience and could ask you personalized, precise, and hard-hitting questions until unique insights started emerging in the conversation.</p>\n<p>Then, like magic, the best content, with sensitive details redacted, was published to LinkedIn on your behalf.</p>\n<p>This would attract interest and engagement, ultimately landing you job offers, new clients, invitations to speak at conferences, and more.</p>\n<p>If I could snap my fingers and provide this service to you today, delivering on those benefits with 100% certainty, what would be an amount of money that would be considered offensive for me to ask for per month?</p>\n<p>(An amount that you would pay but not be thrilled about.)</p>\n<p>Let me know in the comments.</p>\n",
