    "content": "<p>Let's get hands dirty with AI instead of death by PowerPoint...</p>\n<p>Just wrapped an energizing 60-min working session with Justin Burke where we moved from AI theory to practice.</p>\n<p>No slides, no hypotheticals - just real implementation.</p>\n<p>The goal?</p>\n<p>Help Justin create authentic LinkedIn content without the typical blank-page anxiety.</p>\n<p>We cobbled together various AI tools into a voice-based workflow that had him sharing deep insights within minutes.</p>\n<p>Most interesting part?</p>\n<p>The AI interviewer went DEEP.</p>\n<p>It asked follow-up questions I wouldn't have thought of, drawing out Justin's expertise on founder narratives and market positioning.</p>\n<p>Within just a few minutes, we had enough authentic content for multiple posts.</p>\n<p>Justin's first AI-assisted post is already live and gaining traction.</p>\n<p>But more importantly, we proved you can use AI while maintaining authenticity and providing real value.</p>\n<p>Want to see how we did it? Full working session video below üëá</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lnkd.in/e8kZuKdT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://lnkd.in/e8kZuKdT</a></p>\n<p>PS - This is what I mean when I post about \"creating artisanal software\" w/ AI - rapidly prototyping solutions by combining AI tools, then refining based on real user feedback.</p>\n<p>PPS - tools/services used: <a href=\"https://vapi.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vapi</a> Figma Anthropic OpenAI Descript Upwork <a href=\"https://superwhisper.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">superwhisper</a> Fireflies.ai Otter.ai</p>\n<p>Curious about hands-on AI implementation?</p>\n<p>DM me or book a working session through the link in the video.</p>\n<p>#ArtisanalSoftware #BuildInPublic #AIPrototyping</p>\n",
