    "content": "<p>New case study from OpenAI and Upwork where UW has absolutely taken the right approach ‚Äî pushing general purpose tools like <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> Enterprise to their limits rather than relying on separate \"streamlined\" AI products.</p>\n<p>If you want to transform your organization with AI, the very first step is giving everyone access to the basic tooling and seeing what they come up with!</p>\n<p>Beware of vendors who claim otherwise...</p>\n",
