    "title": "Definitely seeing a new AI-native role emerge: someone curious and good at asking questions of top-1% experts within an org to unstick the tacit knowledge in their heads and then encode it into eg a Claude project, custom GPT, application system prompt and scale access.",
    "date": "2024-08-17",
    "content": "<p>Definitely seeing a new AI-native role emerge: someone curious and good at asking questions of top-1% experts within an org to unstick the tacit knowledge in their heads and then encode it into eg a <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> project, custom GPT, application system prompt and scale access.</p>\n<p>If you're not doing this now, you should.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Get ChaGPT Enterprise / Team or <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> Team accounts for some or all of your employees,</li>\n<li>Hire an insatiably curious gen-Z'er with high verbal intelligence,</li>\n<li>Give him or her a company Otter.ai license,</li>\n<li>Negotiate a 30-day goal of 25 interviews recorded & 5 custom GPTs (or <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> projects) derived from those transcripts used daily by other employees (each should have >=1 DAU).</li>\n<li>Have them present their findings and a repository with all the primary source data at a recorded/optional 60m presentation that includes their methodology, findings, outcomes, surprises, next steps, and Q&A.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Voila!</p>\n<p>In just under a month, you're well on your way to cultivating a meaningful data asset and transforming your organization with AI.</p>\n",
