    "title": "One of my favorite real-world \"1,000x\" AI integration examples I like to share is ...",
    "date": "2024-08-03",
    "content": "<p>One of my favorite real-world \"1,000x\" AI integration examples I like to share is going from discovery call to comprehensive proposal in minutes, not days (or weeks):</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Record meeting with Fireflies.ai</li>\n<li>Immediately pop the transcript into <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a>.</li>\n<li>Ask 3 Opus to come up with a proposal outline (use <a href=\"https://superwhisper.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">superwhisper</a> to include your own op-ed that wasn't captured in the meeting via dictation + a couple gold standard proposals, copy-and-pasted from your own private storage into the context window).</li>\n<li>Iterate (again through rapid reading and dictation) 1-2 times until outline content is right.</li>\n<li>Direct <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> to draft each section. (Iterate if necessary.)</li>\n<li>Copy and paste all that text into a Google Doc (or an AI powered equivalent like lex dot page for a handful of copy edits)</li>\n<li>Identify copy and line edits with Grammarly</li>\n<li>Bring the whole thing back into the <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> conversation and prompt it to step into the recipient's shoes, and use step-by-step reasoning to predict the percentage likelihood that they'll take the next step.</li>\n<li>Ask <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> \"what would have to be true?\" to get a 10‚Äì20% probability boost?</li>\n<li>Tell <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> to turn those identified gaps into hard-hitting and precise questions.</li>\n<li>Do research to substantially address each one.</li>\n<li>Take the additional info you've gathered (in whatever form: notes, dictation, copied and pasted material, whatever) and bring it back to <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a>.</li>\n<li>Draft a succinct follow up email with the bespoke proposal and hit send.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Timebox this whole thing to less than an hour (I've done this in literally less than 90 seconds after calls), and then be on your merry way, onto the next item in your work queue...</p>\n<p>The SPEED with which you can turn something like this around is an absolutely enormous advantage versus anyone else who's vying to meet the same need.</p>\n<p>It's almost like you get the advantages of PLG without the crazy capital requirements.</p>\n<p>AI -> velocity & quality (contingent upon skillful data acquisition and direction of the systems).</p>\n<p>The expert version of this is the same, except you get on a call with a partner or distributor who is open to you selling your solution through their platform ‚Äî role play as the final buyer / seller, take the live transcript from Otter.ai, do similar iteration with <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a>, get live feedback from the partner and incorporate it until they're satisfied, and then immediately send them a forward-able email with all the info they need to simply add a one-liner to their client to gauge interest.</p>\n<p>This works for so many other types of content - landing pages, RFPs, job descriptions, you name it ...</p>\n",
    "excerpt": "One of my favorite real-world \"1,000x\" AI integration examples I like to share is going from discovery call to comprehensive proposal in minutes, not days (or...",
