    "title": "2004: you ask search engines questions...",
    "date": "2024-07-24",
    "content": "<ol start=\"2004\">\n<li>you ask search engines questions...</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2024\">\n<li>search engines ask YOU questions!</li>\n</ol>\n<p>This might be AI's most important feature.</p>\n<p>Good questions invite focus and ultimately action.</p>\n<p>So, if these systems are good enough compressors, then with enough context data - with enough high fidelity proprietary data in their context window that's salient to your life and your goals, along with the breadth of its pre-training set and whatever other sources it's able to semi-automatically retrieve from...</p>\n<p>Then, given some specified higher-order goal, it should be able to prompt you into thinking about things in the right way and then taking the right action.</p>\n<p>The search engine that asks you questions.</p>\n<p>The LLM that prompts you.</p>\n<p>The curious AI that uses motivational interviewing to help you accelerate in the right direction!</p>\n",
