    "content": "<p>Here's the deal ‚Äî REAL digital transformation doesn't have to be expensive, time-consuming, or require an army of consultants.</p>\n<p>What if instead of wading through months of PPT, you could instead get results immediately by working with a lean, mean boutique shop that knows how to use generative AI tools across industries and workflows, solves real problems with urgency, and energizes staff?</p>\n<p>Digital transformation is possible, but, in 2024, how you get there looks different, thanks to this new generation of tech...</p>\n<p>Before AI, shipping a 0-1 IT milestone could take months + a team of engineers, designers, product managers, and scrum masters (especially in an enterprise setting).</p>\n<p>But now, that time-to-first-magic-moment can be compressed dramatically ‚Äî all you need is hyper-focused team (maybe just one person!) who pays close attention to user needs and uses SOTA models to build stuff that works NOW.</p>\n<p>As a buyer/executive, consider this your invitation to raise your expectations when working with outside experts on AI integration & digital transformation initiatives...</p>\n<p>That's why I don't charge for discovery ‚Äî AI-native firms like mine can focus on selling outcomes, not billable hours.</p>\n<p>Are you interested in going 0-1 on enterprise AI integrations in hours, not months?</p>\n<p>(And keeping your investors, board, and employees satisfied in the process...)</p>\n<p>Send me a DM.</p>\n",
