    "title": "Think AI is just a fancy Google? Think again.",
    "date": "2024-05-17",
    "content": "<p>Think AI is just a fancy Google? Think again.</p>\n<p>ùóîùóú ùó∂ùòÄùóª‚ÄôùòÅ ùóÆ ùòÄùó≤ùóÆùóøùó∞ùóµ ùó≤ùóªùó¥ùó∂ùóªùó≤; ùó∂ùòÅ‚ÄôùòÄ ùóÆ ùòÅùóµùóºùòÇùó¥ùóµùòÅ ùóΩùóÆùóøùòÅùóªùó≤ùóø.</p>\n<p>Poor queries get poor results. You receive mountains of data that you have to manually comb through before you can even get to identifying potential insights.</p>\n<p>AI thrives on context. Provide it with well-structured questions and sufficient data‚Äîarticles, books, podcasts‚Äîand AI provides you with outputs as actionable insights.</p>\n<p>ùóúùòÅ‚ÄôùòÄ ùóÆ ùòÄùó∂ùó∫ùóΩùóπùó≤ ùó≤ùóæùòÇùóÆùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª: ùóπùó≤ùòÄùòÄ ùòÅùó∂ùó∫ùó≤ ùòÄùó≤ùóÆùóøùó∞ùóµùó∂ùóªùó¥, ùó∫ùóºùóøùó≤ ùòÅùó∂ùó∫ùó≤ ùó≤ùòÖùó≤ùó∞ùòÇùòÅùó∂ùóªùó¥.</p>\n<p>I work alongside startup founders and enterprise CEOs to integrate AI into their business operations, removing points of friction and enhancing their decision-making velocity.</p>\n<p>Let‚Äôs connect and explore how you can turn AI into a real thought partner.</p>\n",
