    "id": "post-2024-05-16-7196962688885751808",
    "title": "ùóúùóª ùóØùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó≤ùòÄùòÄ, ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùó∫ùóÆùóΩ ùó∂ùòÄ ùóªùóºùòÅ ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùòÅùó≤ùóøùóøùó∂ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ.",
    "date": "2024-05-16",
    "content": "<p>ùóúùóª ùóØùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó≤ùòÄùòÄ, ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùó∫ùóÆùóΩ ùó∂ùòÄ ùóªùóºùòÅ ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùòÅùó≤ùóøùóøùó∂ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ.</p>\n<p>Business leaders are often fooled into complacency by systemization in the form of ‚Äúplaybooks‚Äù: commonly-used methods that are systemized and adopted across the industry.</p>\n<p>History shows that just as industries consolidate and playbooks seem to have it all figured out, new technologies emerge to make these playbooks obsolete.</p>\n<p>AI is the latest tech tsunami sweeping away all the old playbooks. The map no longer fits the territory.</p>\n<p>How do you navigate the unmapped frontier of AI? You need an agile and strategic mentality to guide your business through uncertainty.</p>\n<p>ùóòùóªùòÅùó≤ùóø ùó¢ùóØùó∑ùó≤ùó∞ùòÅùó∂ùòÉùó≤ùòÄ ùóÆùóªùó± ùóûùó≤ùòÜ ùó•ùó≤ùòÄùòÇùóπùòÅùòÄ (ùó¢ùóûùó•ùòÄ).</p>\n<p>OKRs are your compass for navigating AI‚Äôs revolution of the business landscape. They give you ample space to de-risk experimentation and make agile moves that balance your ambition while managing risk.</p>\n<p>Balancing quarterly objectives with long-term decision-making gives you stronger feedback loops. Every quarterly OKR cycle provides feedback that allows you to refine your objectives and adjust to market uncertainty in the long run.</p>\n<p>Combined with leveraging the power of AI, you can incrementally reform your business and adjust to this rapidly developing frontier and discuss new synergies between your businesses‚Äô unique capabilities, strong brand, and even entirely new opportunities.</p>\n<p>Remember: each OKR is a multimillion-dollar decision that could define your company's success. If you want to unlock the full potential of OKRs, you need to implement them with deliberation.</p>\n<p>I help startup founders and enterprise CEOs create and execute impactful OKRs. If you're looking to navigate the new AI landscape and want to learn more about how OKRs can help, DM me.</p>\n",
    "excerpt": "ùóúùóª ùóØùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó≤ùòÄùòÄ, ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùó∫ùóÆùóΩ ùó∂ùòÄ ùóªùóºùòÅ ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùòÅùó≤ùóøùóøùó∂ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ. Business leaders are often fooled into complacency by systemization in the form of...",
