    "id": "post-2024-05-08-7193972972833902592",
    "title": "As CEOs, we face the challenge of ‚Äúfocus‚Äù every single day.",
    "date": "2024-05-08",
    "content": "<p>As CEOs, we face the challenge of ‚Äúfocus‚Äù every single day.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Micro decisions</li>\n<li>Information overload</li>\n<li>Unending list of routine tasks</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Lots of things competing for your attention.</p>\n<p>We can‚Äôt ignore these activities.</p>\n<p>But we also can‚Äôt spend too much time on them.</p>\n<p>So, in the spirit of Andy Grove‚Äôs High Output Management, I began incorporating AI into my daily life to try and navigate these activities faster.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>To complete tasks efficiently</li>\n<li>To make high-quality micro decisions quickly</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And now, I can confidently say:</p>\n<p>Leveraging AI in daily life is one of the most powerful habits to build.</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs how you can get started:</p>\n<p>ùü≠. ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùóßùóÆùòÄùó∏ùòÄ:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Where are you spending your attention right now? What repetitive tasks and decisions consume disproportionate amounts of your time?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ùüÆ. ùó¶ùó≤ùóπùó≤ùó∞ùòÅ ùóßùóºùóºùóπùòÄ:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose AI tools that address these specific areas. This could range from simple speech-to-text AI assistants to advanced AI analytics for decision support.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ùüØ. ùóúùóªùòÅùó≤ùó¥ùóøùóÆùòÅùó≤ ùóöùóøùóÆùó±ùòÇùóÆùóπùóπùòÜ:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integrate these tools into your daily routine, starting with simpler tasks and progressively moving to more complex decisions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ùü∞. ùóòùòÉùóÆùóπùòÇùóÆùòÅùó≤ ùóÆùóªùó± ùóîùó±ùó∑ùòÇùòÄùòÅ:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Evaluate the impact on your productivity and decision-making quality. Adjust your tools and approach based on what you learn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ùü±. ùó¶ùó∞ùóÆùóπùó≤ ùóÆùóªùó± ùóòùòÖùóΩùóπùóºùóøùó≤:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>As you become comfortable, explore additional AI applications to further enhance your capabilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Start small.</p>\n<p>Maybe only a couple of real-life use cases.</p>\n<p>(I would start with AI dictation & AI-assisted summaries for long-form content)</p>\n<p>You will:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Upskill</li>\n<li>Save time</li>\n<li>Get better ideas</li>\n<li>Have more energy</li>\n<li>And become significantly more effective</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And I‚Äôm certain, you‚Äôll find AI opportunities in your business too.</p>\n",
