    "id": "post-2024-05-07-7193610608653594624",
    "title": "How to repurpose long-form video content using AI:",
    "date": "2024-05-07",
    "content": "<p>How to repurpose long-form video content using AI:</p>\n<p>Long-form video content is a goldmine.</p>\n<p>You could create:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Blog posts</li>\n<li>Newsletters</li>\n<li>Linkedin articles</li>\n<li>Twitter threads</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now, think of <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> & <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> as 2 freelance writers.</p>\n<p>To start, you can pick 1.</p>\n<p>To take it to the next level, you can use both.</p>\n<p>I recently created blog post drafts using both under the supervision of an expert copywriter.</p>\n<p>And the results were impressive.</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs the process I used:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I generated transcripts of videos using Descript</li>\n<li>I provided the transcript to both AI systems and asked them to write a blog post on a given topic.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>(Copywriter‚Äôs feedback:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> is good with ‚ÄúStructuring‚Äù the content.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> is good with ‚ÄúStyling‚Äù the content.</p>\n<p>So, I continued...)</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>I asked <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> to give me the structure.</li>\n<li>I gave the structure to <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> and asked for a rewrite.</li>\n<li>Finally, I asked the expert to record feedback and gave it to <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> for final iteration.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Note how this is exactly like working with 2 writers.</p>\n<p>We take both writer‚Äôs drafts and pick the best parts from both.</p>\n<p>In the end, the blog post generated was quite good.</p>\n<p>If you have a lot of video content available,</p>\n<p>You can use this process to generate good 1st drafts. (at scale)</p>\n<p>Try it out!</p>\n<p>And let me know how it goes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>PS ‚Äì If you want to test out such AI-assisted content systems, I have 1 FREE slot still open for my AI-power hour calls.</p>\n<p>In the call, we‚Äôll:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Assess the highest leverage AI opportunity</li>\n<li>Build a prototype solution</li>\n<li>Create a roadmap for AI integration</li>\n</ul>\n<p>DM me ‚ÄúAI coach‚Äù if you wanna get started!</p>\n",
