    "title": "3 tips to become AI-powered without wasting time:",
    "date": "2024-05-06",
    "content": "<p>3 tips to become AI-powered without wasting time:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Be clear with your goals</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Don‚Äôt get distracted by shiny objects.</p>\n<p>Goals give you a direction to focus.</p>\n<p>You‚Äôll know what to say ‚Äúno‚Äù to.</p>\n<p>And you‚Äôll generate ideas to create *real* value with AI.</p>\n<p>Clear goals ‚Üí Simple AI integration</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Design small AI experiments</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Progress with AI is incremental.</p>\n<p>Don‚Äôt spend excessive time planning your AI integration.</p>\n<p>Pick low-hanging fruit.</p>\n<p>And try to solve micro problems with custom AI solutions.</p>\n<p>Small experiments ‚Üí More iterations ‚Üí Valuable AI integration.</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Build a culture of asynchronous communication</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Once you find proof, AI can spread like wildfire.</p>\n<p>Async communication will catalyze the spread of new knowledge.</p>\n<p>Teach your team members how to create Loom videos.</p>\n<p>And get them excited to share their AI wins publicly, e.g. internal Slack channels.</p>\n<p>More Loom videos ‚Üí More AI adoption ‚Üí Successful AI integration</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Remember,</p>\n<p>AI will not transform anything overnight.</p>\n<p>But if you implement these 3 tips,</p>\n<p>You will start realizing genuine long-term benefits for your business.</p>\n<p>And build AI solutions that only you can.</p>\n<p>Contingent to your goals :)</p>\n",
