    "title": "My 4-step process to ‚ÄúElectrify‚Äù businesses with generative AI:",
    "date": "2024-04-25",
    "content": "<p>My 4-step process to ‚ÄúElectrify‚Äù businesses with generative AI:</p>\n<p>(developed after 20+ successful AI integration projects)</p>\n<p>üéØ ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùü≠: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùó£ùóºùó∂ùóªùòÅ ùóï (ùòÑùóµùó≤ùóøùó≤ ùòÜùóºùòÇ ùòÑùóÆùóªùòÅ ùòÅùóº ùó¥ùóº)</p>\n<p>Begin by envisioning your desired outcome.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Actionable AI integration starts with clarity over the desired outcome.</li>\n<li>Where are we currently (Point A) & where do we want to be (Point B)</li>\n<li>A strategic goal provides a lens for problem identification, AI tool selection, and decision-making.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Set good goals. THEN, use AI to get there 10 times faster.</p>\n<p>üß± ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùüÆ: ùóóùóøùóÆùòÑ ùóÆ ùóïùóπùòÇùó≤ùóΩùóøùó∂ùóªùòÅ</p>\n<p>The objective is to identify the highest leverage AI opportunity (use-case).</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Using tools like Miro, I draw an end-to-end map of the company's processes.</li>\n<li>This helps visualize the workflow, making it easy to identify where AI can be most useful‚Äîin other words, ‚Äúwhere to install the first AI-as-electricity outlet‚Äù.</li>\n<li>Here, we use the goals we set above to guide the decision-making.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Post blueprinting, the AI opportunity (almost) jumps out at you!</p>\n<p>üïµüèª ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùüØ: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùóîùóú ùòÉùóÆùóªùó¥ùòÇùóÆùóøùó±</p>\n<p>Successful AI transformation requires leadership to drive the change.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI vanguard is your leader who oversees the AI integration process.</li>\n<li>He/She is equipped with resources, authority, and support.</li>\n<li>They have the license to experiment, implement, and scale AI across the business.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This role is crucial. Choose your champion wisely.</p>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùü∞: ùó¶ùòÅùóÆùóøùòÅ ùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùóîùóú</p>\n<p>Now, we build the AI solution that we identified in step 2.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The nature of the solution will be specific to your business.</li>\n<li>One-size fits all approach doesn‚Äôt work.</li>\n<li>I recommend approaching every problem separately and designing tailored AI solutions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Some solutions: Customized prompt library, <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> Pro + Fireflies AI + Superwhisper, artisanal AI software.</p>\n<p>There are many possible types of solutions.</p>\n<p>Nature of the solution doesn‚Äôt matter, as long as it works!</p>\n<p>I‚Äôve implemented this process across 20+ businesses in 10+ industries.</p>\n<p>And we‚Äôve created a long-lasting impact.</p>\n<p>So, I know it works.</p>\n<p>Would you like me to expand on any of the steps?</p>\n",
