    "title": "3 tips for integrating AI into your company culture:",
    "date": "2024-04-23",
    "content": "<p>3 tips for integrating AI into your company culture:</p>\n<p>(and inspire your team to become AI-powered)</p>\n<p>üí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùü≠: ùó¶ùóΩùóºùóªùòÄùóºùóø ùóîùóú ùó∂ùóªùòÅùóøùóºùó±ùòÇùó∞ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ ùòÑùóºùóøùó∏ùòÄùóµùóºùóΩùòÄ</p>\n<p>A workshop is more than just an event.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôs a signal to your team that AI is an important deal.</p>\n<p>When your team witnesses leaders embracing AI, they‚Äôll do the same.</p>\n<p>And an AI workshop is the perfect way to execute this!</p>\n<p>Remember: You are only one ‚ÄúAHA‚Äù moment away from being AI-powered.</p>\n<p>üí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùüÆ: ùó®ùòÄùó≤ ùóüùóºùóºùó∫ ùòÉùó∂ùó±ùó≤ùóºùòÄ ùòÅùóº ùòÄùóΩùóøùó≤ùóÆùó± ùóîùóú ùòÄùòÇùó∞ùó∞ùó≤ùòÄùòÄ</p>\n<p>Success with AI spreads like wildfire.</p>\n<p>So, you must be prepared with a mechanism that allows the wildfire :)</p>\n<p>Educate people on Loom videos & incentivize sharing them.</p>\n<p>Show, don‚Äôt tell.</p>\n<p>Set an example by creating looms yourself & coaching a few people 1:1.</p>\n<p>Before you know it, your entire team will be using AI in ways you never imagined.</p>\n<p>üí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùüØ: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùóîùóú ùòÉùóÆùóªùó¥ùòÇùóÆùóøùó±</p>\n<p>This person will be in charge of the AI bandwagon.</p>\n<p>He/She will experiment with new AI solutions & make them accessible.</p>\n<p>He/She will include AI as part of every weekly review.</p>\n<p>He/She will work directly with you to identify the biggest AI opportunities.</p>\n<p>Incentivize this properly, and your AI vanguard‚Äôs intrinsic motivation will ensure the AI wave spreads through your organization!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Individually, these tips work great.</p>\n<p>But combined, they‚Äôll create a long-lasting change in the business.</p>\n<p>It only takes 1 or 2 solutions.</p>\n<p>After that, your business will never work without AI.</p>\n<p>Think about this: Have humans ever lived without electricity after they experienced it?</p>\n<p>You will sit back and enjoy the show!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>PS ‚Äì Have you conducted AI introductory workshops for your teams yet?</p>\n<p>I‚Äôve done 20+ workshops that my clients have found super valuable.</p>\n<p>We solve one narrow problem.</p>\n<p>We identify early adopters.</p>\n<p>We set the stage for AI.</p>\n<p>If you‚Äôre interested, DM me ‚ÄúAI workshop‚Äù.</p>\n<p>We‚Äôll talk about how we can design one for you :)</p>\n",
    "excerpt": "3 tips for integrating AI into your company culture: (and inspire your team to become AI-powered) üí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùü≠: ùó¶ùóΩùóºùóªùòÄùóºùóø ùóîùóú ùó∂ùóªùòÅùóøùóºùó±ùòÇùó∞ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ...",
