    "date": "2024-04-20",
    "content": "<p>I'm looking for a skilled LinkedIn copywriter or ghostwriter to produce 20 high-quality posts per month, derived from my raw content (videos, meeting transcripts, presentations).</p>\n<p>Key details:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Benchmark cost: $1,000/month for 20 posts (am open to outcome-based comp. as well if you're confident you can deliver)</li>\n<li>Posts require my approval</li>\n<li>Expectation is text, but open to multimedia posts (I have lots of raw material from meeting recordings, monologues, etc.)</li>\n<li>Flexible on process (previously used Taplio to schedule + async comms via Slack & Loom previously)</li>\n<li>Referral bonus: 30% of first month ($300) if you recommend someone I end up working with</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I help executive teams set and pursue good goals on the frontier of their industry, & get there 10X faster with AI.</p>\n<p>Have served clients over the past year and change w/ engagements that were mostly focused on one or the other, but am looking to bring this together cohesively going forward and continue to use LinkedIn as top-of-funnel channel.</p>\n<p>High expectations - I know what's possible with AI. If you're an excellent writer who delivers great results quickly, let's talk!</p>\n<p>Reach out directly here or at christian (at) gsdat (dot) work.</p>\n",
