    "id": "post-2024-04-19-7187087557455753219",
    "title": "AI's capabilities are growing.",
    "date": "2024-04-19",
    "content": "<p>AI's capabilities are growing.</p>\n<p>Pushing beyond simple tasks into the realm of innovation.</p>\n<p>When <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> was released, it could only be used one way.</p>\n<p>You could ask it questions, and get interesting answers.</p>\n<p>But you couldn‚Äôt rely on it for a fruitful conversation.</p>\n<p>Today, <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> is a different weapon.</p>\n<p>You can instruct it to become a serious thought partner.</p>\n<p>To ask you questions to refine your thinking.</p>\n<p>And it becomes a creativity assistant!</p>\n<p>Think about this for a moment.</p>\n<p>This signals a shift in the way we‚Äôll work.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Humans are freed from mundane tasks.</li>\n<li>Humans also can quickly refine their ideas.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Combined, it signals an era of (possibly) unprecedented innovation and breakneck speeds.</p>\n<p>The verdict, to me, is simple:</p>\n<p>The sooner we build healthy relationships with AI-enhanced media, the sooner we'll cultivate the necessary skills and intuition for its most beneficial use.</p>\n<p>So, start experimenting with AI today.</p>\n<p>It doesn‚Äôt matter how small (or even trivial) the task is.</p>\n<p>As I tell all my clients, ‚ÄúIt only takes one AHA moment to unlock a completely new world‚Äù.</p>\n",
