    "id": "post-2024-04-18-7186725203924721664",
    "title": "How to identify ‚ÄúAI as Thought Partner‚Äù opportunities for your business?",
    "date": "2024-04-18",
    "content": "<p>How to identify ‚ÄúAI as Thought Partner‚Äù opportunities for your business?</p>\n<p>(And use AI to assist you in making high-quality decisions)</p>\n<p>AI is excellent at solving the ‚Äúblank page‚Äù problem.</p>\n<p>The dynamic nature of business means:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You‚Äôll face situations you‚Äôve never faced before</li>\n<li>You‚Äôll face problems you‚Äôve never solved before</li>\n<li>You‚Äôll face decisions you‚Äôve never made before</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To confidently make these decisions, you need to research.</p>\n<p>AI acts as an on-ramp to the frontier.</p>\n<p>Reducing your research time.</p>\n<p>By a significant margin.</p>\n<p>Here are 2 questions that‚Äôll help you reveal these opportunities:</p>\n<p>ùóßùóµùóºùòÇùó¥ùóµùòÅ ùó£ùóÆùóøùòÅùóªùó≤ùóø ùó§ùòÇùó≤ùòÄùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùü≠:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What's something that you know you need to figure out, but you don't even know where to start?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[Tip: Compile a list of problems that are outside of your area of expertise and you keep pushing to number two on your to do list. If you‚Äôre a CEO/business owner, you will always have these problems]</p>\n<p>ùóßùóµùóºùòÇùó¥ùóµùòÅ ùó£ùóÆùóøùòÅùóªùó≤ùóø ùó§ùòÇùó≤ùòÄùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùüÆ:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What new topics or skills would help you crush your current business goals? Knowledge that you‚Äôve never found the time to learn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[Tip: Add these topics & skills to the above list]</p>\n<p>Traditionally, you would‚Äôve brought in an expert, to give you specific actionable improvements.</p>\n<p>You still might need to do that.</p>\n<p>But now, you will have a list to start before going to someone.</p>\n<p>I call the list: ‚ÄúAI Thought Partner Starter List‚Äù.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This becomes the starting point now.</p>\n<p>You can use the attached list as an example :)</p>\n<p>Pre-AI world, you would never find the time to research any of them.</p>\n<p>Now, with AI, you can make progress with ALL of them!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Can you immediately think of any opportunities?</p>\n<p>Put them in the comments!</p>\n<p>Would love to brainstorm how we can use AI to take them forward :)</p>\n",
