    "date": "2024-03-07",
    "content": "<p><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>/<a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> vs Custom-built AI Software:</p>\n<p>How to know when you‚Äôre ready for ‚ÄúAI as Electricity‚Äù?</p>\n<p>The primary purpose of AI is to help you get from point A to point B, 10x faster.</p>\n<p>Our game plan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Accurately identify where you are (point A).</li>\n<li>Clarify where you want to go (point B).</li>\n<li>Then, use AI to turbocharge your journey towards the goal.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hence, if you haven‚Äôt crystallized points A & B, take a step back before you move forward :)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now, assuming you have clarity on your goals, here‚Äôs what I recommend:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Start using <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>/<a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> and push it as far as you can.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Break down the goal into micro tasks (the smaller the better)</li>\n<li>Write prompts to train <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>/<a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a></li>\n<li>Give feedback & specific examples</li>\n<li>Build the habit of working with AI</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Using AI effectively is an art.</p>\n<p>And <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>/<a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> are wonderful to get you started.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Once you‚Äôve found a good groove, start optimizing the new process with custom-built AI software</li>\n</ol>\n<p>If you find yourself:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Doing repetitive manual tasks</li>\n<li>Piping data through same repositories</li>\n<li>Using the same prompts again and again</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Essentially, you‚Äôve pushed the limit, but now you want to take it up a notch.</p>\n<p>That‚Äôs when custom-built AI solutions (‚Äúartisanal software‚Äù) come into the picture.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Using <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>/<a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a>, we first find the signal.</p>\n<p>Then, custom-built AI solutions double down on that signal.</p>\n<p>And following this process, you transition from the old-school traditional mode of business to AI-Powered mode of business :)</p>\n",
