    "title": "My 4 step framework that helps me uncover actionable AI use cases for my clients:",
    "date": "2024-02-29",
    "content": "<p>My 4 step framework that helps me uncover actionable AI use cases for my clients:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Get clarity on the Goals</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Ask the question: ‚ÄúIf we could wave a magic wand and achieve one major result in 3 months, what would it be?</p>\n<p>Goals set context for AI integration.</p>\n<p>Once we know where we‚Äôre trying to go, AI then becomes a means by which we get there 10x faster.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Business Blueprinting</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Draw an end-to-end map of the company's processes. I use Miro for this.</p>\n<p>Once we have a visual representation of the company‚Äôs workflows, AI opportunities start jumping out.</p>\n<p>Especially since we‚Äôve clarified what‚Äôs the goal we‚Äôre trying to achieve!</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Identify AI-integration opportunities</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Dig out pain points where AI can effectively eliminate bottlenecks.</p>\n<p>I‚Äôve found 2 lenses to be very effective:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How can we use AI to streamline operations?</li>\n<li>How can we use AI to drive innovation?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If done right, operators buy back time and start working more on energizing activities, delegating draining work to our friendly AI assistants.</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Find the Champion</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Assign the role of AI Champion to an enthusiastic early adopter.</p>\n<p>Fuel their desire to master the craft of AI by giving them the license to experiment.</p>\n<p>Ask them to present their findings in check-in meetings.</p>\n<p>Not only does the champion upskill, but this kick-starts the AI culture within the organization.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>My aim with my clients is to guide them to their first ‚ÄúAHA‚Äù moment with AI.</p>\n<p>Because that‚Äôs all it takes.</p>\n<p>Once they experience the way of working with AI, they never go back!</p>\n<p>What do you think?</p>\n<p>Have you had your first ‚ÄúAHA‚Äù moment yet?</p>\n",
