    "id": "post-2024-02-28-7168605774817009664",
    "title": "Old School Business Owners:",
    "date": "2024-02-28",
    "content": "<p>Old School Business Owners:</p>\n<p>Imagine a traditional industrial factory‚Äî</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Busy, bustling, but with lots of manual hard labor</li>\n<li>100s of people, drenched in sweat, working in the heat.</li>\n<li>Humans are doing everything, even the smallest of tasks.</li>\n<li>Everyone is exhausted, toiling.</li>\n<li>Work feels like Work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nobody has time for innovation.</p>\n<p>The factory cranks out the same stuff for years and years on razor-thin margins.</p>\n<p>If they survive, that‚Äôs a Win.</p>\n<p>AI-Powered Business Owners:</p>\n<p>Imagine an advanced, electricity-run factory ‚Äî</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clean, humming, super-focused, and hyper-productive.</li>\n<li>Machines and robots are working 24*7 x 365.</li>\n<li>Clerical tasks are a thing of the past.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Humans do what only humans can do:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Thinking, Creating, Relating & Orchestrating.</li>\n<li>Work feels like Play.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This factory is constantly innovating, introducing new product lines & buzzing with ever-increasing margins.</p>\n<p>The goal is to push the limits and make progress on the frontier.</p>\n<p>Profits are just a by-product.</p>\n<p>You know which image excites me :)</p>\n",
