    "title": "Smaller businesses might just leverage AI to leap-frog bigger corporations.",
    "date": "2024-02-12",
    "content": "<p>Smaller businesses might just leverage AI to leap-frog bigger corporations.</p>\n<p>We may be experiencing a ‚Äúhistory repeats itself‚Äù moment!</p>\n<p>Back in the 2000s, communications was the frontier.</p>\n<p>The world was moving from the physical wire networks to wireless & satellite-based communications.</p>\n<p>The technology was made available globally.</p>\n<p>And developing nations identified opportunities to skip the wired system entirely!</p>\n<p>As a Result:</p>\n<p>Some developing nations with no ICT infrastructure were able to roll out wireless communications faster than developed nations.</p>\n<p>But why didn‚Äôt the developed nations upgrade at least as quickly?</p>\n<p>Answer ‚Üí The inertia of change management</p>\n<p>Once anything grows in size, it loses its ability to quickly adapt, pivot & start new ways of working. There‚Äôs a deep commitment to a prior paradigm of work that‚Äôs difficult to completely overhaul.</p>\n<p>It happens to startups.</p>\n<p>It happens more to enterprises.</p>\n<p>And it can happen to entire states.</p>\n<p>Today, the same is true with AI.</p>\n<p>AI is globally available.</p>\n<p>AI presents a new way of working.</p>\n<p>AI meets you where you are in your journey of building a business.</p>\n<p>Smaller organizations can now find ways to delegate work to software that was previously not possible. And with nimble, quick-to-adapt teams, you might just have a strategic advantage to make the most of the AI opportunity.</p>\n<p>If you start using AI today:</p>\n<p>By the time enterprises and corporations involve AI in their day-to-day activities, you‚Äôll be miles ahead.</p>\n<p>Just like developing nations did,</p>\n<p>We can embrace the new technology and directly start working with AI.</p>\n<p>The opportunity is as ripe as it has ever been :)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Want more of my insights on leveling up with AI?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow me</li>\n<li>Hit the üîî icon</li>\n<li>Let‚Äôs become AI-enhanced digital workers</li>\n</ul>\n",
