    "id": "post-2024-02-07-7160995719347077121",
    "title": "Last year, I did an AI integration project for an Executive Coaching firm.",
    "date": "2024-02-07",
    "content": "<p>Last year, I did an AI integration project for an Executive Coaching firm.</p>\n<p>The CEO wanted to grow revenue by acquiring new clients (inbound & outbound).</p>\n<p>But he was facing a challenge:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>He needed to activate multiple acquisition channels (Webinars, LinkedIn, Email)</li>\n<li>So, he had to amp-up his content production (by a lot!)</li>\n<li>He and his team, however, were busy serving existing clients.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>It was a perfect opportunity to put AI to work :)</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs what we did:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>AI for Market Research</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>We mined 100s of hours of podcast interviews with AI to identify hot topics for an upcoming webinar.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>AI for Cold Outreach</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>We used AI to accelerate the creation of personalized outreach emails by incorporating AI-assisted analyses of public SEC filings</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>AI for Linkedin Content</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>We worked with AI to take the CEO‚Äôs original ideas, transcribe them, and transform them into compelling multimedia: 20+ text & video LinkedIn posts demonstrating CEO‚Äôs thought leadership to attract inbound leads.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And, did it work?</p>\n<p>Here are the results:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>6 qualified leads</li>\n<li>$7,500 in new revenue (‚Äúthis number should go up‚Äù)</li>\n<li>In 6 months: LinkedIn impressions: 90,000+, Engagements: 1,200+</li>\n</ul>\n<p>But more importantly, the CEO now feels:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>More energized to do the hard work of brand-building on Linkedin</li>\n<li>More excited to create high-quality content by working with AI</li>\n<li>More capable of capturing & sharing new, useful ideas that come during any given day.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>That‚Äôs what a successful AI story looks like to me.</p>\n<p>Yes, the goal is to hit the metrics.</p>\n<p>And if used properly, AI does help you there 10x faster.</p>\n<p>But AI also unlocks a new mode of working where you are more capable, excited & energized.</p>\n<p>These benefits are often intangible but transformational!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>P.S. I‚Äôve been witnessing high demand for custom-designed AI solutions for business.</p>\n<p>So, I‚Äôm opening up 3 slots for my AI integration program. If you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Resonate with all of the above</li>\n<li>Have an established offer for your business</li>\n<li>Have a strategy in place & need to 10x your speed towards the goal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Just DM me ‚ÄúAI coach‚Äù and I‚Äôll get in touch with you!</p>\n",
