    "title": "üí° Last year, one of my most successful clients was a Recruiting & Staffing Agency.",
    "date": "2024-02-01",
    "content": "<p>üí° Last year, one of my most successful clients was a Recruiting & Staffing Agency.</p>\n<p>They were curious about how AI could power up their business.</p>\n<p>In our first business blueprinting session, we identified a bottleneck.</p>\n<p>‚è≥ The recruiters were spending a significant amount of time on administrative tasks like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Taking notes during calls with candidates and clients</li>\n<li>Drafting documents like job descriptions and client presentations</li>\n<li>Manually entering notes into their CRM system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This was draining their energy and taking time away from more strategic tasks.</p>\n<p>Since most of these tasks were already well understood by the client, it presented a wonderful opportunity for AI to power things up!</p>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è We decided to power up their business with a combination of 2 AI solutions.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integrating Read AI to eliminate Note-Taking in meetings</li>\n<li>Custom AI software solution</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The software takes inputs like call transcripts and resumes, and automatically drafts documents like pre-screening call notes, job descriptions, and client presentations that the recruiters then review and finalize.</p>\n<p>üëäüèª Results?</p>\n<p>Recruiters use it over 100 times per month, giving them up to 20% of their time back for more valuable and energizing activities.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>One recruiter went from spending 10-15 minutes on a client presentation to just 2 minutes.</li>\n<li>Another saved over 90% of the time, going from nearly 2 hours down to 20 minutes to draft 10 client presentations</li>\n<li>Another recruiter reported being able to increase the number and quality of candidate phone screens she conducts because, thanks to her AI notetaker, she no longer has to take detailed notes during each call.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>üî• Within just a few weeks of integrating AI into their systems, they‚Äôve unlocked a smarter, more enjoyable, and more effective way of business.</p>\n<p>With the freed-up time, they could focus on more satisfying & strategic tasks (like proactive client outreach) as well as dig deeper into client problems to improve their service offers.</p>\n<p>Overall, since they became AI-Powered, they‚Äôve improved their service quality, increased their throughput, and created a much happier work environment within the team.</p>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è That‚Äôs the magic of AI!</p>\n<p>If you can figure out specific use cases, it‚Äôs possible to create AI solutions that actually work!</p>\n<p>And once you realize the power of working with AI, as my clients have now, there‚Äôs no going back.</p>\n<p>Work becomes fun :)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>üìå PS - I‚Äôve opened up 3 slots for my AI as Electricity program.</p>\n<p>If you‚Äôre:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Curious about how AI can create efficiencies for your business [AND]</li>\n<li>Have a remote team of knowledge workers [AND]</li>\n<li>Have Struggled to leverage AI for business yet effectively</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Just DM me 'I‚Äôm Ready'. We'll have a quick chat around how you can unlock a similar transformation.</p>\n",
