    "date": "2024-01-30",
    "content": "<p>My typical daily AI routine:</p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>00 AM - Wake up and avoid screens for the first 30 minutes.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>It's a time for me to connect with my family and myself, without the digital world intruding.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>00 AM - Dive into strategic work.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Here, I leverage AI for planning and reflection. I record my thoughts on Otter.ai or Scribe while I run through my structured OKR reflection process.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Then I ask <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> to generate insights and follow-up questions. By the end, I‚Äôve reviewed objectives, progress, confidence ratings, and lessons learned.</p>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li>00 AM - Client engagements and workshops.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Preparation is key, and I use AI to significantly enhance the quality of my meetings. I upload relevant context (transcripts, goals, priorities) into <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> & collaborate with it to prepare for meetings. It‚Äôs super effective!</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>00 PM - Post-meeting follow-ups.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>I use Otter to summarize key points and share insights with relevant parties, ensuring that everyone is on the same page.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>00 PM - Afternoons involve reviewing notifications and emails.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Here, I use AI dictation tools to make my communications quick and efficient. I‚Äôve increased my productivity dramatically by combining Whisper & <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Here‚Äôs how it works:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I open all threads, emails & open loops and dictate my answers to Whisper.</li>\n<li>I give <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> this prompt:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>‚ÄúPlease take the transcript above and add whitespace in line breaks for readability‚Äù</p>\n<p>The results are insane!</p>\n<p>Email overwhelm is a relic of the past now. All thanks to AI :)</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>30 PM - Podcasts and learning.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>I use Snipd for quick summaries of podcasts, helping me stay updated with minimal time investment.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>00 PM - Summarize the day</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Engaging with my network and sharing insights on platforms like Twitter, utilizing AI for thoughtful and quick interactions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Evening - Unplugging from technology.</p>\n<p>This balance is crucial for me. It's about spending quality time with family, reading books,  indulging in hobbies, and just being present.</p>\n<p>Total time with AI - Roughly 6 hours.</p>\n<p>I repeat this process daily, with minor tweaks depending on the day's demands.</p>\n<p>Roughly 25-30% of my working time revolves around leveraging AI, and the impact spreads across 100% of activities.</p>\n<p>Overall, the idea is to be intentional with my screen time, and be super efficient while I‚Äôm at it :)</p>\n<p>Works pretty well for me.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Want more of my insights on leveling up with AI?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow me</li>\n<li>Hit the üîî icon</li>\n<li>Let‚Äôs become AI-enhanced digital workers</li>\n</ul>\n",
