    "title": "How I use AI to make better life decisions?",
    "date": "2024-01-26",
    "content": "<p>How I use AI to make better life decisions?</p>\n<p>(by making <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> my thought partner)</p>\n<p>Better life decisions come from developing a better thinking process.</p>\n<p>When you cultivate a broad perspective, you identify multiple possible options.</p>\n<p>This abundance of options leads to creative solutions.</p>\n<p>But the problem is: It‚Äôs not easy to broaden your perspective!</p>\n<p>You need to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Find people to talk to who‚Äôve gone through a similar journey</li>\n<li>Explore your curiosities in diverse fields of knowledge</li>\n<li>Learn from failed experiments</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Previously, this used to take a lot of time.</p>\n<p>But now, we have access to generative AI (<a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>). And it‚Äôs game-changing.</p>\n<p>Here are 4 techniques I use to help me broaden my perspective with <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a>:</p>\n<p>ùü≠/ ùó¶ùó∞ùó≤ùóªùóÆùóøùó∂ùóº ùó¶ùó∂ùó∫ùòÇùóπùóÆùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You could use AI to run through a series of \"If-Then\" narratives based on your current decisions. This could involve career moves, educational opportunities, or personal growth strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Given my current role and skills in [your field], if I pursue an advanced degree in [desired field], what potential career paths could open up for me?</p>\n<p>ùüÆ/ ùóñùóπùóÆùóøùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùó¨ùóºùòÇùóø ùó©ùóÆùóπùòÇùó≤ùòÄ</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI can help you align your decisions with your core values.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I value honesty, innovation, and empathy.</p>\n<p>I‚Äôm going through a transition phase with lots of changes happening. Here‚Äôs a description:</p>\n<p>[Give context by explaining the situation that you‚Äôre currently facing]</p>\n<p>Can you help me identify decisions in my professional life that align with these values?</p>\n<p>[Pro Tip] If you‚Äôre not sure about your core values, take Ben Sands ‚ÄúValue Assessment‚Äù diagnostic test.</p>\n<p>Upload the report and witness how <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> gives you beautiful angles to think about your life decisions :)</p>\n<p>ùüØ/ ùóñùóøùó∂ùòÅùó∂ùó∞ùóÆùóπ ùó•ùó≤ùó≥ùóπùó≤ùó∞ùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Engage with AI to question and challenge your assumptions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I believe that moving to a new city will improve my career prospects.</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs why: [Speak about your situation and explain your reasoning]</p>\n<p>Can you challenge this assumption and propose situations where this might not be the case?</p>\n<p>ùü∞/ ùó†ùó≤ùóªùòÅùóÆùóπ ùó†ùóºùó±ùó≤ùóπ ùó®ùóΩùó±ùóÆùòÅùó≤ùòÄ</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Allow AI to present new information that changes your perspectives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>‚ÄúI'm considering a move to a new city for a job that seems like a great fit for my career goals.</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs why: [Speak about your situation and explain your reasoning]</p>\n<p>Please provide data on the quality of life, cost of living, and career growth opportunities in [target city] compared to my current location.</p>\n<p>Are there potential downsides I may not have considered?</p>\n<p>What strategies could I employ to mitigate possible challenges associated with this move?</p>\n<p>Have a genuine dialogue, treating <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> as a trusted confidant.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôll give you something to think about. I promise :)</p>\n<p>Would you like me to expand on any of these?</p>\n",
