    "id": "post-2024-01-24-7155922275525955585",
    "title": "How to write a good ChatGPT prompt?",
    "date": "2024-01-24",
    "content": "<p>How to write a good <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> prompt?</p>\n<p>(that gives good results for ANY use case)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> is like a recent master‚Äôs grad assistant you‚Äôve hired.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôs super-smart, but also extremely naive.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôll follow instructions & perform tasks very well.</p>\n<p>But ONLY if you can teach it EXACTLY what needs to be done!</p>\n<p>So how do we train our <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> assistant well?</p>\n<p>We need 3 elements.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Context</li>\n<li>Process</li>\n<li>Examples</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Let‚Äôs create a good <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> prompt using the 3 elements.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1Ô∏è‚É£ ùóñùóºùóªùòÅùó≤ùòÖùòÅ - ‚Äúùó™ùóµùóº ùóÆùóøùó≤ ùòÜùóºùòÇ & ùó™ùóµùóÆùòÅ ùó∂ùòÄ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùòÅùóÆùòÄùó∏‚Äù</p>\n<p>You are Email Copywriter GPT.</p>\n<p>You are an expert email copywriter with 10+ years of experience.</p>\n<p>I have written Email sequences for my email list.</p>\n<p>Your task is to help me refine the copy & make it better using proven copywriting principles.</p>\n<p>2Ô∏è‚É£ ùó£ùóøùóºùó∞ùó≤ùòÄùòÄ - ‚ÄúùóõùóºùòÑ ùòÅùóº ùó±ùóº ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùòÅùóÆùòÄùó∏‚Äù</p>\n<p>I'm going to give you inputs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who is my target audience?</li>\n<li>What are the products & services I‚Äôm offering to my clients?</li>\n<li>What is my positioning as a business?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You have to follow these steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Explain your understanding of my business back to me</li>\n<li>Once I‚Äôm happy, I‚Äôll give you the green light. Then you ask me for emails one by one.</li>\n<li>I‚Äôll give you the email</li>\n<li>You have to read the email & give me a detailed breakdown of the email along with actionable advice on where the copy can be improved.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>3Ô∏è‚É£ ùóòùòÖùóÆùó∫ùóΩùóπùó≤ùòÄ - ‚Äúùó™ùóµùóÆùòÅ ùó±ùóºùó≤ùòÄ ùóÆ ùó¥ùóºùóºùó± ùóøùó≤ùòÄùóΩùóºùóªùòÄùó≤ ùóπùóºùóºùó∏ ùóπùó∂ùó∏ùó≤‚Äù</p>\n<p>You must give me your breakdown in the following format.</p>\n<p>Rating of the copy (0/10):</p>\n<p>Why?:</p>\n<p>What actionable advice would you give to bump up the rating:</p>\n<p>Specific sections where these improvements can be implemented:</p>\n<ol>\n<li></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Before Section ‚Üí</p>\n<p>After Section rewritten with improvement ‚Üí</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Before Section ‚Üí</p>\n<p>After Section rewritten with improvement ‚Üí</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>No matter what use case, if you write a good prompt‚Äîjust like giving clear directions to that recent Masters grad‚Äîyou will get good responses.</p>\n<p>Try it out with different types of problems: those where you know how to do something specific, don‚Äôt want to do it anymore, but it needs to get done regularly.</p>\n<p>Once you start getting into a habit of AI delegation, work becomes efficient & fun!</p>\n<p>Let me know if you find something :)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>PS- If you‚Äôre having trouble finding these use cases for your business, I wrote a 5-Day Educational Email course just for you.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôll give you everything you need to start identifying endless opportunities to use AI.</p>\n<p>Get it here: startusingai.carrd.co</p>\n",
