    "id": "post-2024-01-23-7155559962805477376",
    "title": "I like playing the game of Entrepreneurship on Hard mode.",
    "date": "2024-01-23",
    "content": "<p>I like playing the game of Entrepreneurship on Hard mode.</p>\n<p>Value >>> everything else.</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs how I design my client engagements:</p>\n<p>ùü≠/ ùó¶ùó∞ùóºùóΩùó≤ ùóÆ ùóΩùóøùóºùóØùóπùó≤ùó∫, ùó£ùó∂ùòÅùó∞ùóµ ùóÆ ùòÄùóºùóπùòÇùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª</p>\n<p>Beginning of every client engagement, I present a slide with 4 titles.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Outcomes (What are we trying to achieve?)</li>\n<li>Outputs (What will you get at the end?)</li>\n<li>Agenda (How will we get there?)</li>\n<li>Time (How much time will it take?)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For Example:</p>\n<p>Here‚Äôs how I structured one of my 2-hour ‚ÄúIntroduction to AI‚Äù paid consulting projects:</p>\n<p>(The client was curious about how they could use AI to power up their business)</p>\n<p>Outcome ‚Üí XXX team makes meaningful progress on a strategic objective by using AI to create a deliverable and/or increase process efficiency AND, as a consequence, participants gain confidence that they‚Äôll use AI to become more productive over the next 3 months</p>\n<p>Outputs ‚Üí Recordings, transcripts, scratch pad, code (a mini software)</p>\n<p>Agenda & Time‚Üí</p>\n<p>Intro [5 mins]</p>\n<p>AI toolkit overview: Landscape with capabilities and caveats [10 mins]</p>\n<p>Sizzler [10 mins]</p>\n<p>Deep-Dive: Building a mini custom AI software to solve a specific problem [90 mins]</p>\n<p>Recap + next steps [10 mins]</p>\n<p>This helps both me & client have extreme clarity about everything we‚Äôre doing together.</p>\n<p>ùüÆ/ ùóñùóÆùòÄùóµ ùòÇùóΩùó≥ùóøùóºùóªùòÅ ùòÑùó∂ùòÅùóµ ùó¶ùóÆùòÅùó∂ùòÄùó≥ùóÆùó∞ùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùóöùòÇùóÆùóøùóÆùóªùòÅùó≤ùó≤</p>\n<p>The handshake deal with clients is:</p>\n<p>‚ÄúAt any point in time, if you do not feel I‚Äôm providing the value I promised, you can call off the engagement and I‚Äôll give you a pro-rated refund. No questions asked.‚Äù</p>\n<p>This unlocks 3 benefits:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Cash upfront forces both parties to become focused on the outcome.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>An investment makes you invested in the result. Hence, we move 10x faster.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Satisfaction Guarantee forces me to be confident in the results I deliver</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>If I‚Äôm unsure about my skills/ability to deliver, I won‚Äôt make the pitch to begin with!</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>I take up Zero outside funds to run the business</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>After shutting down my equity-financed startup, I‚Äôve made profitability the North Star.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Playing the game on hard mode forces me to up-skill as an entrepreneur with every new client engagement.</p>\n<p>Yes, it‚Äôs not easy, and sometimes feels like I am taking it to extremes.</p>\n<p>But it has been a fantastic catalyst for my learning, especially with generative AI.</p>\n<p>The constraints help me unlock the creativity required to push the boundaries of what's possible with a brand-new technology. (without wasting my or client‚Äôs time)</p>\n<p>And, last but not least,  this mode of Entrepreneurship has unlocked a beautiful freedom that allows me to work on my interests and earn a living while doing so.</p>\n<p>Truly grateful and truly excited for everything to come :)</p>\n",
    "excerpt": "I like playing the game of Entrepreneurship on Hard mode. Value >>> everything else. Here‚Äôs how I design my client engagements: ùü≠/ ùó¶ùó∞ùóºùóΩùó≤ ùóÆ...",
    "type": "post",
    "originalUrl": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7155559962805477376"
