    "date": "2023-12-02",
    "content": "<p>Last month, my client cracked a 100% boost in productivity after plugging AI into their business. But this wasn‚Äôt the best part!</p>\n<p>2 hidden benefits delighted the CEO even more üëáüèª</p>\n<ol>\n<li>‚ÄúNo note-taking in 1-1 meetings. It‚Äôs incredibly better to just be present in the conversation and let AI do the typing.‚Äù</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Tips for CEOs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install Read.ai/Otter.ai & start transcribing your meetings</li>\n<li>Feed the transcript to <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> (or <a href=\"https://claude.ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Claude</a> or Otter AI Chat)</li>\n<li>Ask <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> to summarize, derive insights, point inconsistencies, identify opportunities, and anything useful.</li>\n<li>Give <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> a blank structure + 1 example. It‚Äôll instantly convert the transcript into beautiful meeting notes.</li>\n<li>Now you can pay closer attention to the content, observe subtle cues of other attendees, and identify deeper client needs while your assistant does the note-taking.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>‚ÄúOne person on the team was initially cautious & afraid. Now she‚Äôs like, this is tremendous.‚Äù</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Tips for CEOs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Identify 1 activity that is central to operations but is tedious to perform manually</li>\n<li>Figure out the information flow: Input ‚Üí Process ‚Üí Output</li>\n<li>Explain this process to <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> and provide 3-4 varied examples</li>\n<li>Try your <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> prompts & give feedback to make it better</li>\n<li>Make a video on Loom to explain your process to the team</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once your team starts using AI, they‚Äôll be happier & more productive.</p>\n<p>Or, as my client says:</p>\n<p>‚ÄúPandora‚Äôs box has been opened now & I can‚Äôt go back‚Äù</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I specialize in integrating AI into your Business to help you save time, grow revenues & beat the competition. 2 slots have just opened up in my schedule.</p>\n<p>Who I work with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SMB Business Owners with Remote Teams (10-200 employees)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want the AI transformation, DM me ‚ÄúAI‚Äù and we‚Äôll have a quick chat!</p>\n",
