    "title": "When technology suddenly starts doing *absurd* stuff, it‚Äôs a sign that things are about to change!",
    "date": "2023-11-29",
    "content": "<p>When technology suddenly starts doing *absurd* stuff, it‚Äôs a sign that things are about to change!</p>\n<p>It‚Äôs in those first magic moments with a revolutionary technology that you realize something special is about to happen.</p>\n<p>Think: Web Browser in 1993, AI in 2022.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôs when you realize that something that was literally impossible now suddenly becomes possible.</p>\n<p>For example, in just 4‚Äì5 minutes, I can create a custom commercial for your company, where your latest and greatest product line gets pitched by your favorite actor.</p>\n<p>(I recently did this during a live client workshop with...Ryan Reynolds.)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>üìå [Here‚Äôs the secret recipe for the magic show]</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Take all copy from your company website</li>\n<li>Copy the transcript of a Ryan Reynolds commercial</li>\n<li>Paste it all into a <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> chat</li>\n<li>Use AI to clone Ryan‚Äôs voice in just a few clicks via ElevenLabs</li>\n<li>Create images using Midjourney and FaceSwapID</li>\n<li>Turn the images into videos using D-ID, Kaiber, and RunwayML</li>\n<li>Edit the video & add subtitles using Descript</li>\n<li>As a bonus: add a custom soundtrack with MusicGen</li>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è The advent of generative AI is truly a zero-to-one moment.</p>\n<p>It‚Äôs making something that was previously impossible, possible.</p>\n<p>People routinely expect incremental improvements, like a 20-30% boost in efficiency.</p>\n<p>But in truth, infinite improvements are possible for some tasks because you‚Äôre dividing by zero.</p>\n<p>We can now do things we could not imagine before.</p>\n<p>That‚Äôs incredible!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>üí° And that‚Äôs the point behind the Ryan Reynolds commercial.</p>\n<p>Do we use it for our marketing?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Definitely not ‚Äî but it certainly gets the creative gears turning‚Ä¶</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I love sharing these magic moments with clients in real-time to demonstrate that AI can open up entirely new possibilities for their business.</p>\n<p>Things that we couldn‚Äôt even imagine before!</p>\n<p>So, set ambitious goals and start experimenting with AI.</p>\n<p>You never know when you‚Äôll stumble onto a massive breakthrough :)</p>\n",
