    "id": "post-2023-11-28-7135266150732435456",
    "title": "One big false belief I see among knowledge workers is, ‚ÄúAI will take away my job‚Äù.",
    "date": "2023-11-28",
    "content": "<p>One big false belief I see among knowledge workers is, ‚ÄúAI will take away my job‚Äù.</p>\n<p>That‚Äôs NOT true. Here‚Äôs how I think about this ‚Üí</p>\n<p>AI will not replace you.</p>\n<p>But, with AI as your sidekick, you might buy back 50-80% of your time.</p>\n<p>ü§î Imagine this:</p>\n<p>A recent graduate of a master's degree program volunteers to work for you.</p>\n<p>They work 24*7 and never complain.</p>\n<p>And while they‚Äôre a hard worker, they‚Äôre also a bit na√Øve!</p>\n<p>üßëüèª‚Äçüíª Now, when you start your day:</p>\n<p>You can delegate half of the tasks on your to-do list to your assistant.</p>\n<p>And they‚Äôll never be upset when you delegate more things that you don‚Äôt want to do.</p>\n<p>Won‚Äôt you be happy to have someone like that working for you (and nearly for free)?</p>\n<p>üëâüèª The truth is:</p>\n<p>There's an art and science to working with AI.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI won‚Äôt do everything that you want to do</li>\n<li>AI won‚Äôt do everything that you DON‚ÄôT want to do either</li>\n</ul>\n<p>It really is like a recently graduated master‚Äôs student who‚Äôs eager to please.</p>\n<p>üôÅ But it‚Äôll make mistakes. You‚Äôll need to check it‚Äôs work.</p>\n<p>Over time,</p>\n<p>You‚Äôll learn to delegate higher proportions of support tasks that come bundled with your job.</p>\n<p>So that you free up more time to achieve higher levels of mastery in things that energize you.</p>\n<p>üí° That‚Äôs the actual goal. Isn‚Äôt it?</p>\n<p>AI won‚Äôt take away your job.</p>\n<p>AI will make you more effective.</p>\n<p>But you‚Äôll have to learn the art and science of working with AI.</p>\n<p>And like any positive change, this will take time :)</p>\n<p>So, if you‚Äôve been *secretly* putting off AI for a while, take this as your trigger to start today!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>**</li>\n</ul>\n<p>P.S ‚Äì If you don‚Äôt know where to start, I‚Äôve built an AI crash course just for you!</p>\n<p>This email course gives you everything you need to install AI and start using it confidently.</p>\n<p>The course launches on Friday (2 days to go!).</p>\n<p>Comment ‚ÄúAI Electricity‚Äù and I‚Äôll add you to the waitlist!</p>\n",
