    "id": "post-2023-11-11-7128958660084412416",
    "title": "Last week, President Biden issued an Executive Order on Artificial Intelligence.",
    "date": "2023-11-11",
    "content": "<p>Last week, President Biden issued an Executive Order on Artificial Intelligence.</p>\n<p>Already, federal agencies have identified >700 AI use cases, from \"Autonomous Situational Awareness\" for U.S. Department of Homeland Security to \"Smart Wildlife Tracking\" for U.S. Department of the Interior.</p>\n<p>So, I created a custom GPT that helps anyone dig into the data and learn about how USG is starting to think about AI.</p>\n<p>It will even illustrate the most interesting use cases for you to give you an idea what each would look like in practice!</p>\n<p>See for yourself ‚Äî and, if something piques your interest, just ask it how you can contribute your own expertise to the government-wide AI talent surge...</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lnkd.in/eBiRECvf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://lnkd.in/eBiRECvf</a></p>\n",
