    "id": "post-2023-08-21-7099446132686102528",
    "title": "‚ÄúYou've really opened my eyes to what's possible when you reduce the time-to-capability side of the equation‚Ä¶‚ÄäThat surprised me the most.",
    "date": "2023-08-21",
