    "title": "Are you completely undervaluing artificial intelligence by thinking about it as simply something that makes you and your team more efficient?",
    "date": "2023-07-09",
    "content": "<p>Are you completely undervaluing artificial intelligence by thinking about it as simply something that makes you and your team more efficient?</p>\n<p>Here's why you should consider a different perspective...</p>\n<p>I like to use three metaphors to understand the influence and potential of AI:</p>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è as electricity: ubiquitous, present in everything, with a utility-like business model</p>\n<p>üôã‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è as an assistant: a naive yet eager-to-please analyst or scribe, enhancing our efficiency</p>\n<p>üß† as a thought partner: not just answering our queries but asking questions that push the boundaries of our individual expertise and align with our intrinsic motivations and insatiable curiosity</p>\n<p>The first two metaphors cover AI‚Äôs capabilities well, but it‚Äôs the third - AI as a thought partner - where I see tremendous untapped potential. AI as a thought partner enables us to explore areas of uncertainty more quickly and can be a powerful catalyst for innovation and value creation, going beyond mere efficiency.</p>\n<p>With the <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> iOS app‚Äôs integration of Whisper, which allows for highly accurate transcription and interaction with GPT-4 through natural language, AI is not just lowering the cost of information retrieval, repackaging, and prediction...</p>\n<p>It can also challenge you, aiding your discursive reasoning and turbocharging your creative process to help you think think things through as you work through problems at the frontier of your expertise.</p>\n<p>Ready to use AI to become not only more efficient, but also MORE EFFECTIVE?</p>\n<p>Start by opening <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ChatGPT</a> Plus, rambling about a topic that's top of mind, and then ask GPT-4 to start asking YOU questions‚Ä¶</p>\n<p>#AI #Innovation #FutureTech</p>\n",
