    "content": "<p>Are you ready to participate in the \"exaptive economy\"?</p>\n<p>At the coming intersection of AI, spatial computing, and blockchain technology, I believe that we'll find ourselves working together in entirely new ways‚Äîways that allow for a more just balance between private gain and public good and catalyze an unprecedented explosion in global (and perhaps even interplanetary) innovation.</p>\n<p>In the weeks ahead, I'll be bringing these ideas down to earth with concrete recommendations in individual pieces written for business leaders, knowledge workers, and \"artisanal experts\" who want to flourish in this next era.</p>\n<p>Big thanks to Janet Hall for a fantastic discussion that inspired me to write this piece (and then providing feedback that helped me get it into shape for publication).</p>\n<p>#innovation #ai #technology #blockchain #augmentedreality</p>\n",
