    "title": "For the longest time, I struggled in my love/hate relationship with tech...",
    "date": "2023-02-13",
    "content": "<p>For the longest time, I struggled in my love/hate relationship with tech...</p>\n<p>As productive as I could be with my MacBook and iPhone, it was also all too easy to get distracted by all the shiny digital objects competing for my attention as I tried to get stuff done.</p>\n<p>And making the switch to remote work only made this worse.</p>\n<p>As a resource-constrained startup founder, I realized that these distractions weren't just a nuisance; they were totally unacceptable.</p>\n<p>Finally, after years of experimentation, I figured out a robust solution.</p>\n<p>By making a few simple changes on my phone and laptop, I've fundamentally transformed my relationship with my devices.</p>\n<p>Instead of seeing them as untrustworthy digital casinos‚Äîportals to attention-hungry digital monsters with insatiable appetites for human attention‚ÄîI now treat them as simple tools, trustworthy partners that act in service to my real-world goals.</p>\n<p>When I work with early-stage startup founders who also want to regain their attention and stay hyper-focused online, the very first thing I do is walk them through the same changes I made.</p>\n<p>I call it my \"slot machine-to-toaster\" checklist.</p>\n<p>Because when you use your toaster, you want it to toast toast. You don't want to be bombarded with ads and algorithmically curated content that distracts you from enjoying breakfast.</p>\n<p>Why should your expectations with your digital devices be any different?</p>\n<p>Now, I'm making that checklist available for just $0.99!</p>\n<p>Ready to get your attention back and make it 10x easier to focus while getting more done than ever?</p>\n<p>Get it here: <a href=\"https://lnkd.in/eUpH6iMm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://lnkd.in/eUpH6iMm</a></p>\n<p>#productivity #focus #remotework #attention\",<a href=\"https://3893865824845.gumroad.com/l/reftf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://3893865824845.gumroad.com/l/reftf</a>,\",MEMBER_NETWORK</p>\n",
