    "id": "post-2022-11-28-7003085277082574849",
    "title": "Next time you reach for your phone, pause and ask yourself, ‚ÄúWhat am I really looking for?",
    "date": "2022-11-28",
    "content": "<p>Next time you reach for your phone, pause and ask yourself, ‚ÄúWhat am I really looking for?‚Äù</p>\n<p>When we‚Äôre bored, we take stock of our pasts and plan for the future.</p>\n<p>But in an age of digital distraction, boredom is in short supply‚Äîno wonder it often feels like we‚Äôre stuck in an eternal present.</p>\n<p>The key to thriving in the superabundant digital age is not to use technology to do more with less, but rather to do less but better.</p>\n<p>Excellent words of wisdom from Manoush Zomorodi !</p>\n<p>#technology #digital #attention</p>\n",
