    "content": "<p>Want to learn how VC-backed founders manage their time and stay focused?</p>\n<p>Listen in to an expert panel of entrepreneurs & MIT Sloan School of Management alumni on the evening of Monday the 28th via the new LinkedIn audio event feature.</p>\n<p>40m for panel discussion and 20m for Q&A.</p>\n<p>Add üî• questions about time & attention management in the comments below, and we'll make sure they get answered live by panelists!</p>\n<p>#management #entrepreneurs #founders #timemanagement</p>\n",
